special_powers.name: ASGARDIAN ARMOR
special_powers.description: Once per game, when Thor would be dealt damage, you may instead give him an action token. If you do, Thor ignores that damage.

special_powers.name: MIGHTY MJOLNIR
special_powers.description: Give Thor a power action and make a ranged combat attack. This attack generates knock back, but this knock back path is not stopped by walls or squares of blocking terrain. Instead, destroy that terrain and knock back damage from this attack equals 1 damage plus 1 for each wall or squares of blocking terrain the character moved through.

special_powers.name: SHIELD WALL
special_powers.description: When Einherjar is adjacent to a friendly character named Einherjar, modify both their defense values by +1 if not already modified by this effect.

special_powers.name: DRIVEN
special_powers.description: When Dark Elf Soldier would be dealt pushing damage, roll a d6. On a result of [d:4]-[d:6], ignore that pushing damage.

special_powers.name: MICRO BLACK HOLE BURST
special_powers.description: Dark Elf Soldier can use Incapacitate. This attack has an area of effect including all opposing characters adjacent to the target. In addition to the normal effects, all hit characters halve their speed values until your next turn.

special_powers.name: HARROW RIDER
special_powers.description: Dark Elf has [cs:wing] and can use the Ram ability. When he uses Ram, his movement may be made up of 2 direct paths.

special_powers.name: THE AETHER AND I ARE ONE
special_powers.description: Characters hit by an attack from Malekith can't use defense powers until their next turn.

special_powers.name: LAST STAND
special_powers.description: Malekith can use Super Senses and Toughness.

special_powers.name: MISTRESS OF THE BLADE
special_powers.description: Sif can use Invulnerability. When Sif is adajcent to a friendly character named Thor, he can use Shape Change, but only succeeds on a result of [d:6].

special_powers.name: MY LORD...MY LOVE
special_powers.description: Sif can use Invulnerablility. When Sif is adajcent to a friendly character named Thor, he can use Shape Change, but only succeeds on a result of [d:6].

special_powers.name: NONE SO SHARP AS ASGARDIAN STEEL
special_powers.description: When Sif makes a close combat attack, she may target all adjacent opposing characters. If she does, the damage dealt by the attack can be divided in any way among the successfully hit targets, provided that all damage dealt is divided among them.

special_powers.name: WAR-BRINGER
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, all friendly characters within 6 squares, which are 100 points or less and have both the Asgardian and Warrior keywords can use Sidestep, and modify their damage values by +1 this turn.

special_powers.name: NONE CAN STAND AGAINST ME
special_powers.description: Tyr can use Quake. When he does, his damage value becomes 3 and is locked.

special_powers.name: BATTLE IS WHERE I BELONG
special_powers.description: Tyr can use Invulnerability. When Tyr is targeted with a close combat attack, modify his defense value by +1 for each adjacent opposing character.

special_powers.name: FOCUSED HATRED
special_powers.description: Kurse can use Battle Fury.

special_powers.name: ALGRIM REBORN
special_powers.description: If Kurse enters play through the Battlefield Promotion ability, he is KO'd if he crosses the red KO line. When a countdown click is showing, Kurse can't be moved, placed, targeted, or damaged and at the end your turn, turn this dial once to the right. If all characters friendly to Kurse are KO'd, all countdown clicks become KO clicks. This ability can't be ignored.

special_powers.name: BATTLEFIELD PROMOTION: REBORN AS KURSE
special_powers.description: When Algrim would take 3 or more damage from an attack, you may replace him with [set:tdw] #008 Kurse on his orange starting line. When Algrim would be KO'd, roll a d6, and add the amount of damage he has just taken. On a result of 7 or more, replace him with [set:tdw] #008 Kurse on his orange starting line instead.

special_powers.name: FAR SIGHT
special_powers.description: Heimdall can use Super Senses.

special_powers.name: ACTIVATE THE BIFROST
special_powers.description: Heimdall can use Telekinesis. If an opposing character moved or was placed adjacent to Heimdall since your last turn, Heimdall can use Telekinesis as a free action, but may only use it to place that opposing character.

special_powers.name: I SEE ALL THINGS
special_powers.description: Heimdall can use Perplex and Probability Control as if he had a range value of 8. When he does, he can use [it:hindering,characters].

special_powers.name: WARRIORS THREE
special_powers.description: Friendly characters with the Warriors Three keyword marked with one action token can use Sidestep.

special_powers.name: JUST A FEINT!
special_powers.description: Fandral can use Blades/Claws/Fangs. Once per turn, if he uses it and the hit target takes less than 2 damage, another friendly characters may immediately make a close combat attack targeting the same character as a free action.

special_powers.name: IMPRISONED BY GREED...
special_powers.description: As long as Loki is on a countdown click, he can’t be moved, placed, targeted, assigned an action, or damaged, and at the beginning of your turn, you may turn his dial once to the right. If Loki is on a countdown click and no other friendly characters are on the map on non-countdown clicks, click Loki to click #4.

special_powers.name: ...FREED BY GRIEF
special_powers.description: When this power is first revealed, you may place Loki adjacent to an opposing character that has hit a character that is both friendly to Loki and 30 points or more. When you do, Loki may use Pulse Wave as a free action.

special_powers.name: AFTER ALL, I AM THE GOD OF LIES
special_powers.description: Loki can use Probability Control and Shape Change. When Loki uses Shape Change and the result is [d:6], deal the attacker 1 unavoidable damage after actions resolve.

special_powers.name: LORD OF THE DARK ELVES
special_powers.description: Malekith can use Leadership. When he does and the result is [d:6], you may choose to not remove an action token and instead modify an adjacent friendly character's combat values by +1 until the beginning of your next turn.

special_powers.name: AETHER-ENHANCED POWER
special_powers.description: Malekith can use Penetrating/Psychic Blast and Pulse Wave.

special_powers.name: ILLUSIONS AND DECEPTION
special_powers.description: Malekith can use Perplex and Shape Change. When he uses Shape Change and succeeds, place a Deceived token on the attacker's character card. Malekith may use Mind Control as a free action targeting any number of characters marked with Deceived tokens. Remove all Deceived tokens from characters hit by this use of Mind Control.

special_powers.name: A MOTLEY ARMY FROM ALL NINE REALMS
special_powers.description: When building your force, if Duhg is the highest-point character, other characters that share a keyword with him also have the Duhg's Army keyword.

special_powers.name: GATHERING THE MARAUDERS
special_powers.description: Duhg can use Invulnerability and Mastermind.

special_powers.name: THE WARRIORS THREE
special_powers.description: Friendly characters with the Warriors Three keyword can use Empower, but only to affect characters with the Warriors Three keyword.

special_powers.name: MASTER OF ALL WEAPONRY
special_powers.description: Hogun can use Super Strength but can't pick up or hold heavy or special objects. When he makes a close combat attack while holding an object, roll a d6. On a result of [d:1] through [d:3], he can use Precision Strike. On a result of [d:4] through [d:6], the object is not removed after the attack and Hogun continues to hold it.

special_powers.name: BATTLEFIELD MEDICINE
special_powers.description: Hogun can use Regeneration and Support.

special_powers.name: THE WARRIORS THREE
special_powers.description: Friendly characters with the Warriors Three keyword can use Mastermind. When they do, they may only transfer damage to other characters with the Warriors Three keyword, but they may do so regardless of their point values.

special_powers.name: ONE LAST FEAST WITH FRIENDS
special_powers.description: Once per game, give Volstagg a double power action that deals no pushing damage. Heal all adjacent friendly characters of damage equal to 2 minus the number of action tokens they have and, when Volstagg next clears action tokens, heal him to click #4. Other friendly characters with the Warriors Three keyword are considered adjacent during this action.

special_powers.name: TRUE LION OF ASGARD
special_powers.description: Volstagg can use Defend and Invulnerability.

special_powers.name: STRONGEST OF THE ASGARDIANS
special_powers.description: Thor can use Super Strength. Give Thor a close combat action and, if he hits, you may roll a d6. If the result is greater than the damage taken, replace him with [set:tdw] #001 Thor on the same click number +1.

special_powers.name: GODLY STAMINA
special_powers.description: Thor begins the game with two Stamina tokens on his card. When Thor would take pushing damage, you may instead remove a Stamina token and ignore the pushing damage.

special_powers.name: MIGHTY SWING
special_powers.description: Thor can use Precision Strike and Quake.

special_powers.name: DEFENDER OF THE NINE REALMS
special_powers.description: Thor can use Super Strength and adjacent friendly characters can use Toughness. Once per turn, Thor can use Defend.

special_powers.name: ASGARDIAN FURY
special_powers.description: Thor can use Charge and Flurry.

special_powers.name: CALL DOWN THE LIGHTNING
special_powers.description: Give Thor a ranged combat action and he can use [it:characters] for this action. The area of effect for this ranged attack is any one square within range and line of fire and each square adjacent to it. A hit character occupying the chosen square is dealt Thor's printed damage value. Other hit characters are dealt Thor's printed damage -1.

special_powers.name: GUNGNIR
special_powers.description: Once per game, give Odin a double power action and make a ranged combat attack targeting the highest-point opposing character anywhere on the map. For this attack, Odin's combat values are locked, the attack can't be evaded and the attack roll can't be rerolled by friendly characters. After actions resolve, deal Odin 1 unavoidable damage.

special_powers.name: WHOSOEVER HOLDS THIS HAMMER...
special_powers.description: Thor can use Charge. He can use it normally, or when he is given an action to use Charge, if he moves in a direct line, he can use [im:characters] and, after actions resolve, each character occupying a square that Thor moved through is dealt 1 damage, assigned an action token, and you may place it in a square adjacent to their current position.

special_powers.name: GOD OF THUNDER
special_powers.description: Thor can use Energy Explosion. When he is given a ranged combat action, you may lock his damage value and, if you do, all hit characters are also given an action token.

special_powers.name: AVERSION TO IRON
special_powers.description: When Malekith is dealt damage and the attacker rolled a d6 for Blades/Claws/Fangs for the attack, damage dealt can't be reduced below 1.

special_powers.name: AWAY FROM ME, ASGARDIAN!
special_powers.description: Malekith can use Force Blast and Sidestep.

special_powers.name: THE DECEIVER
special_powers.description: Malekith can use Mastermind, Shape Change, and Super Senses.

special_powers.name: ILLUSORY DUPLICATES
special_powers.description: Loki can use Shape Change and Toughness. When he uses Shape Change and succeeds, Loki may be placed in a square of hindering terrain within 3 squares and line of fire. If the attack was a close combat attack, the attacker's action resolves immediately.

special_powers.name: POWER OF THE AETHER
special_powers.description: Opposing characters hit by Dark Elf Scout's ranged combat attack can't use the Flight ability until your next turn.

special_powers.name: MINION: ASGARDIAN RECONNAISSANCE
special_powers.description: If a friendly character named Malekith is within 8 squares, Dark Elf Scout can use Enhancement.

special_powers.name: UNBREAKABLE ARMOR
special_powers.description: Kurse's defense powers can't be countered.

special_powers.name: THE WILD HUNT
special_powers.description: During your first turn, choose an opposing character. Kurse can use Charge. He can chose to use it normally, or he may choose to not halve his speed value from Charge, but may then only make close combat attacks against the chosen opposing character during that action.

special_powers.name: HORDE: TO ARMS ASGARD!
special_powers.description: When stacked, Einherjar Captain can use Leadership. When (M), Einherjar Captain can use Empower.

special_powers.name: HORDE: MARCH!
special_powers.description: When stacked, other friendly characters whose name contains the word Einherjar and are adjacent to Einherjar Lieutenant at the beginning of the turn modify their speed value by +2 this turn.

special_powers.name: HORDE: STAND TOGETHER
special_powers.description: When stacked, at the beginning of your turn, roll a d6. If that roll is equal to or less than (S), Einherjar Soldier can use Flurry. When (M), Einherjar Soldier can use Combat Reflexes.

special_powers.name: HORDE: FOLLOWING ORDERS
special_powers.description: When (M) and within 8 squares of a character named Einherjar Captain or Einherjar Lieutenant, Einherjar Trainee may be given a close combat action as a free action.

special_powers.name: HORDE: PUSH BACK THE LINE
special_powers.description: When stacked and using Charge, characters that take damage are knocked back (S) squares.

special_powers.name: HORDE: RECONNAISANCE
special_powers.description: When (M), opposing characters within 3 squares can't use Stealth.

special_powers.name: HORDE: OVERWHELM
special_powers.description: When stacked, at the beginning of the turn roll a d6. If the result is equal to or less than (S), modify Dark Elf Soldier's attack and damage values by +1.

special_powers.name: HORDE: STRENGTH IN NUMBERS
special_powers.description: When stacked, Dark Elf can use Empower. When (M), close combat attacks deal penetrating damage.

special_powers.name: Interdimensional Portal
special_powers.description: Orange squares are Portal squares. Portal squares are hindering terrain. For other exciting scenarioes, check the scenario sheet included in this starter!
